 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/ugyorg.showPublicProfile>Gyorg</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Global Rogue</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/8/00 1:24:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wow</span><hr size=1> Thankyou for the compliment Peleas.  They don't call us rogues for nothin.  Most of us may be completely trustable most of the time, but the same way a wizzie will ice comet a kill they want, or a single necro will camp a room that would hold 2 or 3 people, we just play our part. <p><B>Gyorg Lavode</B>, Rogue of the 24rd Moon over Xegony<br>
